HEADWORD: Dialyze
<hw>Di"a*lyze</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Dialyzed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
